                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18060219-8-defend112 t18060219-8-punish41"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>, aged 17.</p>
               <p>[The prisoner was recommended to mercy by the jury, on account of his youth and good character.]</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Heath.</p>
